snippet.title: Super Mario Apocalypse Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After almost 4 years (yes really) of on and off work, it's finally done.
I hope you all enjoy :)
Download link: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1PwOrQ1rtWOFX-R7w7L9tidWrqWeHjN5j

Trailer song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bte_xQVg7-Y

Playlist of every song used in the game: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLMt1VFw95EKxJifYU00NiHS30poQrprFf

A few additional notes:
There are a total of 92 stars in the game. The number of stars required to be the game is 55.
There is no Course 10 in the game. For some reason, I couldn't import over it.
This game is fairly cryptic and puzzle based. Be sure to read every sign and talk to every NPC for clues, plus some of the dialogue is just amusing to read.
This game overall has a very high difficulty so be prepared!
